Package: nids-config
Version: 1.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Maayan App Developer <mapelboim@gmail.com>
Depends: bash, procps, coreutils
Description: NIDS Network Configuration Utility.
 This package installs the nids-config script used to set essential 
 IPv4 and IPv6 kernel parameters required for a robust Network 
 Intrusion Detection System environment.
 